	(463085, 'Dice Horde', 2026, 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/RI65YpqKmDaTyDbZfsUc9Q__small/img/1OeIcCbEIUst6o9hVGSY6qsONjk=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic9369051.jpg', 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/RI65YpqKmDaTyDbZfsUc9Q__original/img/b0U7zPRy1KKFiXbfbONlxHlIPBM=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic9369051.jpg', 1, 1, 30, 60, 60, 0.00, 'Dice Horde, is a solo tower defense roll-and-write where you lead the charge against a wild incursion of dice-headed beasts bursting through fresh rifts to crash your last bastion!

Coming to Kickstarter February 24th 2026!

Each round starts with a dice roll that sets the horde''s march: those cube-headed critters pushing forward like they''re late for a raid.
The same roll hands you your defenses &ndash; quick battlements, quirky ward-towers, and gadgets thrown together by frantic engineers &ndash; all to keep the tide from flooding your stronghold.

Enemies arrive as dice marching across your board, their pips driving the assault: higher numbers send them charging ahead fast-most of the time-slamming your nearest tower like a horde storming the gates.

But you''re in control! Chip away at their values with attacks to slow ''em down and knock ''em out. When a die drops to zero, it tumbles into the graveyard &ndash; your handy pile of shattered bits and odds and scraps.

Collect those pieces to boost upgrades, spring sneaky traps, shore up barricades, or rally elite guards. Master the dice-tweaking tango against these rift-spilling fiends, and you could slam those portals shut. Mess it up? The Dice Horde overruns everything, turning your realm into a really big mess!

Sharpen your pencil, shake those cubes, man the walls and defend your kingdom!

