	(439306, 'Limit', 2025, 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/IJL7RD5VVO6yh7sbhT983g__small/img/-_pU1Y8uSWIl_kbcwXHKg3bcMVE=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic8808756.jpg', 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/IJL7RD5VVO6yh7sbhT983g__original/img/bi5_4_bwSIKeRhAs7AE6RCypQ0s=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic8808756.jpg', 1, 6, 60, 150, 150, 3.33, 'Limit is a competitive strategy game where you play as a Nation facing the challenges of our world. Make crucial political decisions, manage your resources with finesse, anticipate global crises and adapt to the upheavals of the planet and the decisions of other Nations. Balance growth and resilience to build a prosperous society.

The game takes place in a maximum of 7 generations. However, the end of the game can come before if you and your opponents trigger at least 4 global crises.

A generation is made up of 3 phases:


     The Political phase: you make decisions
     The Social phase: your Nation reacts to these decisions
     The International phase: crises arise and alliances are formed


End of the Game:
Before counting your points, you must test the resilience of your Nation for future generations. Redo the Food, Consumption and Production stages of the Social phase with the effects of shortages but without new crises.

