	(440136, 'Labyrinth: Chronicles', 2026, 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/EfGy1i7YAi9BK2nMlM_3Fw__small/img/GzuRPdyTXQSHlZ46jq_e1T6Wg0Y=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic8735490.png', 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/EfGy1i7YAi9BK2nMlM_3Fw__original/img/NYvN19V3A8ytWzFvK-lLyerXMtg=/0x0/filters:format(png)/pic8735490.png', 2, 4, 20, 60, 60, 0.00, 'Once upon a time, there was a Labyrinth, a magical place full of wonders and mysteries. Adventurers who returned told unbelievable stories of its ever-changing walls and shifting corridors, a mind-boggling challenge indeed that only the bravest could tackle. But it was worth it, they say, as the dark nooks of the Labyrinth hide real treasures. The Labyrinth waits for you. Are you brave enough to enter?

