	(447570, 'Mythologies', 2026, 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LmogQFHcVtMonS4OlYn7Zw__small/img/aSaezkTl55bIzO4ACkX3uMOmmTc=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic8916698.jpg', 'https://cf.geekdo-images.com/LmogQFHcVtMonS4OlYn7Zw__original/img/I5_d5oC-v1i2KiW6WSP0Z5nABSc=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic8916698.jpg', 2, 4, 20, 40, 40, 0.00, 'In Mythologies, you are the founder of a young civilization, drawing spiritual strength and power from the mythologies of the world.

Build your own pantheon by invoking gods and legendary creatures from cultures across the globe &mdash; Greek, Egyptian, Norse, Hindu, Zulu, and more &mdash; and earn their favor in your race to divine supremacy.

Each game begins with a unique combination of four mythologies, creating a &ldquo;Sanctuary&rdquo; where players will compete to select powerful entities. You''ll use your strategic wits to draft cards, invoke deities, activate special abilities, and complete divine trials. But choose carefully: placing a card might grant immediate rewards, but those depend on the pantheon level the card is placed in, and sometimes you need to sacrifice your creatures for a greater gain.

Throughout four fast-paced rounds, you&rsquo;ll tactically deploy your chosen beings into your pantheon grid, managing resources while triggering synergies and stacking combos. Draft wisely, balance strategy with sacrifice, and unleash divine powers to complete trials and outwit your rivals.
With every game offering 70 different setup combinations of asymmetric mythologies, quick turns, and rich combos, Mythologies delivers epic replayability in just 30 minutes.

Will your civilization ascend to legend &mdash; or be forgotten among the myths?

